{"type":"message","id":"99d1f61d","parentId":"f66feeba","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:18:19.941Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"[[reply_to_current]] **agent-browser** 已经安装好了（版本 0.20.14）！\n\n这是一个浏览器自动化工具，支持以下功能：\n\n## 基本用法\n\n```bash\n# 打开网页\nagent-browser open https://example.com\n\n# 获取页面元素快照\nagent-browser snapshot -i\n\n# 点击元素\nagent-browser click @e1\n\n# 填写表单\nagent-browser fill @e2 \"输入内容\"\n\n# 截图\nagent-browser screenshot page.png\n```\n\n## 实际例子\n\n```bash\n# 1. 打开百度\nagent-browser open https://www.baidu.com\n\n# 2. 获取可交互元素（会显示 @e1, @e2 等引用）\nagent-browser snapshot -i\n\n# 3. 在搜索框输入内容\nagent-browser fill @e1 \"OpenClaw\"\n\n# 4. 点击搜索按钮\nagent-browser click @e2\n\n# 5. 截图保存结果\nagent-browser screenshot baidu_search.png\n```\n\n不过我刚注意到 **Chrome 安装失败了**（网络问题），这可能会影响使用。你可以：\n\n1. 手动安装 Chrome 或 Chromium\n2. 或者使用 `--headed` 参数用系统自带的浏览器\n\n需要我帮你测试一下具体的功能，或者解决 Chrome 安装的问题吗？","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来测试一下 agent-browser 的具体功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:15","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"agent-browser open https://www.baidu.com 2>&1","shell":"zsh","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773721080479}}
