{"type":"message","id":"d401c7ef","parentId":"1e7db828","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:42:16.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"安装进度：\n- Playwright Chromium 已下载完毕 ✓\n- agent-browser 技能已安装 ✓\n- Chrome 路径已确认：`$HOME/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac/Chromium.app/Contents/MacOS/Chromium`\n\n当前问题：\n- Chrome 可执行文件路径不存在（目录结构可能不同）\n- agent-browser 进程残留导致 socket 占用\n\n让我检查实际目录结构并修复：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:118","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208 -type f -name \"*Chromium*\" -o -name \"*chrome*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10","shell":"zsh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:119","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/","shell":"zsh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:120","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac/Chromium.app/Contents/MacOS/ 2>/dev/null || find ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208 -type f -perm +111 | head -5","shell":"zsh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:121","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && curl -L -o chrome-mac-arm64.zip \"https://storage.googleapis.com/chrome-for-testing-public/133.0.6943.141/mac-arm64/chrome-mac-arm64.zip\" 2>&1 | tail -5 && ls -la chrome-mac-arm64.zip","shell":"zsh","timeout":180}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:122","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 清理环境\nrm -rf ~/.agent-browser\npkill -9 -f \"agent-browser\" 2>/dev/null\npkill -9 -f \"Chromium\" 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\n\n# 查找 Playwright 的 Chromium\nCHROME=$(find ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright -name \"Chromium\" -type f 2>/dev/null | head -1)\necho \"Found Chrome: $CHROME\"\n\nif [ -z \"$CHROME\" ]; then\n    echo \"Chromium not found, installing...\"\n    npx playwright install chromium 2>&1\n    CHROME=$(find ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright -name \"Chromium\" -type f 2>/dev/null | head -1)\nfi\n\necho \"Using Chrome: $CHROME\"\nls -la \"$CHROME\" 2>&1 | head -3","shell":"zsh","timeout":120}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:123","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser/SKILL.md","limit":100}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:124","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 1. 彻底清理环境\nrm -rf ~/.agent-browser\npkill -9 -f \"agent-browser\" 2>/dev/null\npkill -9 -f \"Chromium\" 2>/dev/null\nsleep 2\n\n# 2. 确认 Chromium 实际路径\necho \"=== 查找 Chromium ===\"\nfind ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright -name \"Chromium\" -type f 2>/dev/null\n\n# 3. 检查 chromium-1208 目录结构\necho \"\"\necho \"=== chromium-1208 目录结构 ===\"\nls -la ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/ 2>/dev/null\n\n# 4. 尝试找到可执行文件\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 查找所有可执行文件 ===\"\nfind ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208 -type f -perm +111 2>/dev/null | head -10","shell":"zsh","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773722459758}}
