{"type":"message","id":"1e5527fc","parentId":"860fb7a5","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:42:26.931Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:123","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: Agent Browser\ndescription: A fast Rust-based headless browser automation CLI with Node.js fallback that enables AI agents to navigate, click, type, and snapshot pages via structured commands.\nread_when:\n  - Automating web interactions\n  - Extracting structured data from pages\n  - Filling forms programmatically\n  - Testing web UIs\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🌐\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"node\",\"npm\"]}}}\nallowed-tools: Bash(agent-browser:*)\n---\n\n# Browser Automation with agent-browser\n\n## Installation\n\n### npm recommended\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g agent-browser\nagent-browser install\nagent-browser install --with-deps\n```\n\n### From Source\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-browser\ncd agent-browser\npnpm install\npnpm build\nagent-browser install\n```\n\n## Quick start\n\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>        # Navigate to page\nagent-browser snapshot -i       # Get interactive elements with refs\nagent-browser click @e1         # Click element by ref\nagent-browser fill @e2 \"text\"   # Fill input by ref\nagent-browser close             # Close browser\n```\n\n## Core workflow\n\n1. Navigate: `agent-browser open <url>`\n2. Snapshot: `agent-browser snapshot -i` (returns elements with refs like `@e1`, `@e2`)\n3. Interact using refs from the snapshot\n4. Re-snapshot after navigation or significant DOM changes\n\n## Commands\n\n### Navigation\n\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>      # Navigate to URL\nagent-browser back            # Go back\nagent-browser forward         # Go forward\nagent-browser reload          # Reload page\nagent-browser close           # Close browser\n```\n\n### Snapshot (page analysis)\n\n```bash\nagent-browser snapshot            # Full accessibility tree\nagent-browser snapshot -i         # Interactive elements only (recommended)\nagent-browser snapshot -c         # Compact output\nagent-browser snapshot -d 3       # Limit depth to 3\nagent-browser snapshot -s \"#main\" # Scope to CSS selector\n```\n\n### Interactions (use @refs from snapshot)\n\n```bash\nagent-browser click @e1           # Click\nagent-browser dblclick @e1        # Double-click\nagent-browser focus @e1           # Focus element\nagent-browser fill @e2 \"text\"     # Clear and type\nagent-browser type @e2 \"text\"     # Type without clearing\nagent-browser press Enter         # Press key\nagent-browser press Control+a     # Key combination\nagent-browser keydown Shift       # Hold key down\nagent-browser keyup Shift         # Release key\nagent-browser hover @e1           # Hover\nagent-browser check @e1           # Check checkbox\nagent-browser uncheck @e1         # Uncheck checkbox\nagent-browser select @e1 \"value\"  # Select dropdown\nagent-browser scroll down 500     # Scroll page\nagent-browser scrollintoview @e1  # Scroll element into view\nagent-browser drag @e1 @e2        # Drag and drop\nagent-browser upload @e1 file.pdf # Upload files\n```\n\n### Get information\n\n```bash\nagent-browser get text @e1        # Get element text\nagent-browser get html @e1        # Get innerHTML\n\n[229 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773722546918}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a9a9d9d","parentId":"1e5527fc","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:42:26.937Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:124","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 查找 Chromium ===\n\n=== chromium-1208 目录结构 ===\ntotal 0\ndrwx------  5 liyue  staff  160 Mar 17 12:28 .\ndrwx------  6 liyue  staff  192 Mar 17 12:28 ..\n-rw-------  1 liyue  staff    0 Mar 17 12:28 DEPENDENCIES_VALIDATED\n-rw-------  1 liyue  staff    0 Mar 17 12:26 INSTALLATION_COMPLETE\ndrwx------  6 liyue  staff  192 Mar 17 12:26 chrome-mac-arm64\n\n=== 查找所有可执行文件 ===\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Resources/install.sh\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Libraries/libEGL.dylib\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Libraries/libvk_swiftshader.dylib\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Libraries/libGLESv2.dylib\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Google Chrome for Testing Framework\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/web_app_shortcut_copier\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Plugin).app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Plugin)\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Alerts).app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Alerts)\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/Google Chrome for Testing Helper.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing Helper"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2219,"aggregated":"=== 查找 Chromium ===\n\n=== chromium-1208 目录结构 ===\ntotal 0\ndrwx------  5 liyue  staff  160 Mar 17 12:28 .\ndrwx------  6 liyue  staff  192 Mar 17 12:28 ..\n-rw-------  1 liyue  staff    0 Mar 17 12:28 DEPENDENCIES_VALIDATED\n-rw-------  1 liyue  staff    0 Mar 17 12:26 INSTALLATION_COMPLETE\ndrwx------  6 liyue  staff  192 Mar 17 12:26 chrome-mac-arm64\n\n=== 查找所有可执行文件 ===\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Resources/install.sh\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Libraries/libEGL.dylib\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Libraries/libvk_swiftshader.dylib\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Libraries/libGLESv2.dylib\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Google Chrome for Testing Framework\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/web_app_shortcut_copier\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Plugin).app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Plugin)\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Alerts).app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing Helper (Alerts)\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/Frameworks/Google Chrome for Testing Framework.framework/Versions/145.0.7632.6/Helpers/Google Chrome for Testing Helper.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing Helper","cwd":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773722546925}}
{"type":"message","id":"a31532a3","parentId":"4a9a9d9d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:43:18.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Chromium 已下载，agent-browser 安装完成。但下载任务很多被中断了。我需要向用户总结目前的安装状况，并提供下一步的操作。\n\n现在的情况：\n1. Chromium 已下载到 `~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/`\n2. agent-browser 已安装，版本 0.20.14\n3. Chrome 路径已找到\n\n我需要直接说明当前状态，并提供简化的测试命令，避免再次超时。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，更新一下安装进度：\n\n**✅ 已完成：**\n1. **agent-browser** 已安装（版本 0.20.14）\n2. **Chromium 浏览器** 已下载到 `~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/`\n3. **可执行文件路径** 已找到：\n   ```\n   ~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\n   ```\n\n**⚠️ 遇到的问题：**\n- Playwright 下载被多次中断（网络问题）\n- agent-browser 在连接 socket 时遇到了一些问题\n\n---\n\n现在让我用一个简化的方式来演示 agent-browser 的用法："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:125","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/test_agent_browser.sh","content":"#!/bin/zsh\n# agent-browser 测试脚本\n\n# 设置 Chrome 路径\nexport CHROME_PATH=\"$HOME/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\"\n\necho \"=== 测试 1: 打开百度 ===\"\nagent-browser open https://www.baidu.com --executable-path \"$CHROME_PATH\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 测试 2: 获取页面可交互元素 ===\"\nagent-browser snapshot -i\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 测试 3: 截图 ===\"\nagent-browser screenshot /tmp/baidu.png\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 测试 4: 关闭浏览器 ===\"\nagent-browser close\n\necho \"\"\necho \"测试完成！截图保存在 /tmp/baidu.png\"\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:126","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/agent_browser_demo.md","content":"# Agent Browser 使用指南\n\n## 安装状态\n\n✅ **已安装**\n- agent-browser v0.20.14\n- Chromium 浏览器（Playwright 版本）\n\n## 基本命令\n\n### 1. 打开网页\n```bash\nexport CHROME_PATH=\"$HOME/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\"\n\nagent-browser open https://www.baidu.com --executable-path \"$CHROME_PATH\"\n```\n\n### 2. 获取页面元素\n```bash\nagent-browser snapshot -i\n```\n\n### 3. 点击元素\n```bash\nagent-browser click @e1\n```\n\n### 4. 填写表单\n```bash\nagent-browser fill @e2 \"要输入的文字\"\n```\n\n### 5. 截图\n```bash\nagent-browser screenshot /tmp/page.png\n```\n\n### 6. 关闭浏览器\n```bash\nagent-browser close\n```\n\n## 完整示例\n\n见 `test_agent_browser.sh` 文件\n\n## 注意事项\n\n1. 每次使用都需要指定 `--executable-path` 参数\n2. 使用 `--headed` 参数可以显示浏览器窗口（用于调试）\n3. 如果 socket 报错，运行 `agent-browser close` 清理\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773722546935}}
