{"type":"message","id":"25ca5ad9","parentId":"e2f405bd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:45:49.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经创建了测试脚本和使用文档。现在来总结一下 agent-browser 的情况：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:127","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/agent-browser-summary.md","content":"# Agent Browser 技能安装总结\n\n## 安装状态\n\n### ✅ 已完成的步骤\n\n1. **agent-browser CLI 已安装**\n   - 版本: 0.20.14\n   - 安装路径: `/opt/homebrew/bin/agent-browser`\n   - 安装命令: `npm install -g agent-browser`\n\n2. **Chromium 浏览器已下载**\n   - 位置: `~/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/`\n   - 可执行文件: `chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing`\n\n3. **测试脚本已创建**\n   - 文件: `test_agent_browser.sh`\n   - 使用指南: `agent_browser_demo.md`\n\n### ⚠️ 注意事项\n\n1. **Chrome 路径问题**\n   - agent-browser 的 `install` 命令无法自动下载 Chrome（网络问题）\n   - 需要使用 Playwright 安装的 Chromium\n   - 每次运行都需要指定 `--executable-path` 参数\n\n2. **Socket 问题**\n   - 如果之前运行失败，可能会留下僵尸 socket 文件\n   - 解决方法: `rm -rf ~/.agent-browser/`\n\n3. **权限问题**\n   - 首次运行 Chrome 可能需要用户授权\n\n## 基本使用方法\n\n```bash\n# 设置 Chrome 路径\nexport CHROME_PATH=\"$HOME/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\"\n\n# 打开网页\nagent-browser open https://www.baidu.com --executable-path \"$CHROME_PATH\"\n\n# 获取页面元素\nagent-browser snapshot -i\n\n# 点击元素（使用 snapshot 返回的 @e1, @e2 等引用）\nagent-browser click @e1\n\n# 填写表单\nagent-browser fill @e2 \"要输入的文字\"\n\n# 截图\nagent-browser screenshot /tmp/page.png\n\n# 关闭浏览器\nagent-browser close\n```\n\n## 文件清单\n\n- `/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/test_agent_browser.sh` - 测试脚本\n- `/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/agent_browser_demo.md` - 使用指南\n- `/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/agent-browser-summary.md` - 本文件\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:128","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/quick-test.sh","content":"#!/bin/zsh\n# Quick test for agent-browser\n\n# 清理环境\nrm -rf ~/.agent-browser\npkill -9 -f \"agent-browser\" 2>/dev/null\npkill -9 -f \"Chromium\" 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\n\n# 设置 Chrome 路径\nexport CHROME_PATH=\"$HOME/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\"\n\necho \"Chrome path: $CHROME_PATH\"\necho \"Chrome exists: $(test -f \"$CHROME_PATH\" && echo \"YES\" || echo \"NO\")\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 创建测试页面\necho '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head><title>Agent Browser Test</title></head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Hello from Agent Browser!</h1>\n  <p>If you can see this, agent-browser is working correctly.</p>\n  <button id=\"test-btn\">Test Button</button>\n  <input type=\"text\" id=\"test-input\" placeholder=\"Type here\" />\n</body>\n</html>' > /tmp/agent-test.html\n\necho \"1. Opening test page...\"\nagent-browser open file:///tmp/agent-test.html --executable-path \"$CHROME_PATH\" 2>&1\nsleep 2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"2. Getting interactive elements...\"\nagent-browser snapshot -i 2>&1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"3. Taking screenshot...\"\nagent-browser screenshot /tmp/agent-test-result.png 2>&1\nls -la /tmp/agent-test-result.png 2>&1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"4. Closing browser...\"\nagent-browser close 2>&1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Test Complete ===\"\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:129","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773722599005}}
