{"type":"message","id":"2bee62ab","parentId":"1bc08c6a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:41:16.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]从日志看，我发现了问题：\n\n**日志显示：** `feishu/core/lark-client: feishu: disconnecting WebSocket (accountId=default)`\n\n飞书 WebSocket 连接已经断开了。这通常有几种原因：\n\n## 当前状态\n- ✅ OpenClaw gateway 运行正常\n- ✅ 飞书插件已正确加载\n- ❌ WebSocket 连接已断开\n\n## 问题分析\n日志中只有一个断开事件，没有具体错误信息。常见原因：\n\n1. **飞书开发者后台配置问题**\n   - 需要确认是否开启了 **\"使用长连接接收事件/回调\"**\n   - 需要确认事件订阅地址是否配置正确\n\n2. **鉴权问题** - App ID 或 App Secret 不正确\n\n3. **网络问题** - 无法连接到飞书服务器\n\n让我先重启 gateway 看看能否重新连接：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zrkdl0kx4h7c2qem5w4mx2nd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart 2>&1 && sleep 5 && openclaw gateway status 2>&1","shell":"zsh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773740467561}}
{"type":"message","id":"8687f097","parentId":"2bee62ab","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:42:10.970Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 17:42 GMT+8] OpenClaw 飞书通道session直接不回了"}],"timestamp":1773740530963}}
