{"type":"message","id":"7bd63b80","parentId":"a40c4512","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:42:39.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]看了日志，**现在飞书 WebSocket 连接已经成功建立了！**\n\n最后几条日志显示：\n```\n[info]: [\n  '[ws]',\n  'receive events or callbacks through persistent connection only available in self-build & Feishu app, Configured in:\\n' +\n    '        Developer Console(开发者后台) \\n' +\n    '          ->\\n' +\n    '        Events and Callbacks(事件与回调)\\n' +\n    '          -> \\n' +\n    '        Mode of event/callback subscription(订阅方式)\\n' +\n    '          -> \\n' +\n    '        Receive events/callbacks through persistent connection(使用 长连接 接收事件/回调)'\n]\n[info]: [ '[ws]', 'ws client ready' ]\n```\n\n✅ **ws client ready** - WebSocket 已经连接成功了！\n\n现在你可以：\n1. 在飞书中发送消息 @ OpenClaw 机器人\n2. 我应该能收到并回复了\n\n刚才是 gateway 重启了一次，现在已经重新连接成功。你试试在飞书发个消息看看能不能收到回复？\n\n## 当前配置检查：\n- ✅ App ID / App Secret 已配置\n- ✅ 连接模式: websocket\n- ✅ 飞书插件已加载\n- ✅ WebSocket 连接已建立\n- ✅ 权限配置：允许 `ou_7f5c8f2774475eabd071360f959caf5e` 对话"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773740545547}}
