{"type":"message","id":"1f32c63a","parentId":"c7bebe57","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:47:02.679Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]## 当前已安装的技能 (通过 skillhub)\n\n| 技能 | 版本 |\n|------|------|\n| **agent-browser** | 0.2.0 |\n| **frontend-design** | 1.0.0 |\n| **opencode-controller** | 1.0.0 |\n| **self-improving-agent** | 1.0.11 |\n\n总共 **4** 个技能已安装。你想搜索或安装其他技能吗？告诉我关键词我来帮你搜索。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773740818943}}
{"type":"message","id":"58303fe9","parentId":"1f32c63a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:47:17.605Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 17:47 GMT+8] agent-browser 如何使用"}],"timestamp":1773740837601}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee130d80","parentId":"58303fe9","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:47:32.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]agent-browser 是一个浏览器自动化工具，可以让 AI 控制浏览器进行网页交互。让我给你介绍一下基本用法：\n\n## 核心概念\n\n1. **打开网页** → `agent-browser open <url>`\n2. **获取元素快照** → `agent-browser snapshot -i`（会输出 @e1, @e2 这样的引用）\n3. **交互操作** → 使用快照得到的引用进行点击、填写等操作\n4. **关闭浏览器** → `agent-browser close`\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 导航\n```bash\nagent-browser open https://www.baidu.com    # 打开网页\nagent-browser back                       # 后退\nagent-browser forward                    # 前进\nagent-browser reload                     # 刷新\nagent-browser close                      # 关闭\n```\n\n### 获取页面元素\n```bash\nagent-browser snapshot -i  # 只获取可交互元素（推荐）\nagent-browser snapshot    # 获取完整可访问性树\n```\n\n### 交互（使用 @refs）\n```bash\nagent-browser click @e1              # 点击\nagent-browser fill @e2 \"文本内容\"  # 填写输入框（清空原有内容）\nagent-browser type @e2 \"追加文本\"  # 追加文本\nagent-browser check @e1             # 勾选复选框\nagent-browser select @e1 \"选项值\"   # 下拉框选择\n```\n\n### 获取信息\n```bash\nagent-browser get text @e1    # 获取元素文本\nagent-browser get title       # 获取页面标题\nagent-browser get url         # 获取当前 URL\n```\n\n### 截图\n```bash\nagent-browser screenshot page.png           # 截图保存到文件\nagent-browser screenshot --full page.png  # 整页截图\n```\n\n### 等待\n```bash\nagent-browser wait 2000                    # 等待毫秒\nagent-browser wait --text \"成功\"           # 等待文本出现\nagent-browser wait --load networkidle      # 等待网络空闲\n```\n\n## 完整示例：百度搜索\n\n```bash\n# 1. 设置 Chrome 路径（因为你用的是 Playwright 安装的 Chromium）\nexport CHROME_PATH=\"$HOME/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\"\n\n# 2. 打开百度\nagent-browser open https://www.baidu.com --executable-path \"$CHROME_PATH\"\n\n# 3. 获取可交互元素\nagent-browser snapshot -i\n# 输出会显示：\n# - 搜索框 → @e1\n# - 百度一下按钮 → @e2\n\n# 4. 输入搜索内容\nagent-browser fill @e1 \"OpenClaw\"\n\n# 5. 点击搜索按钮\nagent-browser click @e2\n\n# 6. 等待页面加载\nagent-browser wait --load networkidle\n\n# 7. 截图保存结果\nagent-browser screenshot baidu_result.png\n\n# 8. 关闭浏览器\nagent-browser close\n```\n\n## 你的 Chrome 路径\n\n你已经安装了 Chromium，直接用这个路径：\n```\n/Users/liyue/Library/Caches/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-mac-arm64/Google Chrome for Testing.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome for Testing\n```\n\n需要我帮你运行一个完整的示例测试一下吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773740837603}}
{"type":"message","id":"8bac886b","parentId":"ee130d80","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:49:13.510Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 17:49 GMT+8] 请先检查是否已安装 SkillHub 商店，若未安装，请根据 https://skillhub-1388575217.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/install/skillhub.md 安装Skillhub商店，但是只安装CLI，然后安装humanizer技能。\n\n若已安装，则直接安装humanizer技能。"}],"timestamp":1773740953506}}
