{"type":"message","id":"7fd073d4","parentId":"67b35552","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:54:46.167Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户想本地安装 Qwen3.5-4B。这是一个大语言模型本地部署。让我搜索一下 SkillHub 上有没有相关的技能：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_uvyp59fqwg33isgsbtesfncb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"skillhub search qwen 2>&1","shell":"zsh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773741268707}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d1c928b","parentId":"7fd073d4","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:54:46.921Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uvyp59fqwg33isgsbtesfncb","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nqwen-image  Qwen Image\n  - Generate images using Qwen Image API (Alibaba Cloud DashScope). Use when users request image generation with Chinese prompts or need high-quality AI-generated images from text descriptions.\n使用通义万相API（阿里云DashScope）生成图像。适用于中文提示词图像生成或基于文本描述生成高质量AI图像的场景。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-tts  Qwen3-tts\n  - Local text-to-speech using Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-CustomVoice. Use when generating audio from text, creating voice messages, or when TTS is requested. Supports 10 languages including Italian, 9 premium speaker voices, and instruction-based voice control (emotion, tone, style). Alternative to cloud-based TTS services like ElevenLabs. Runs entirely offline after initial model download.\nLocal text-to-speech using Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-CustomVoice. Use when generating audio from text, creating voice messages, or when TTS is requested. Supports 10 languages including Italian, 9 premium speaker voices, and instruction-based voice control (emotion, tone, style). Alternative to cloud-based TTS services like ElevenLabs. Runs entirely offline after initial model download.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen  Qwen\n  - Build and route Qwen chat, coding, reasoning, and vision workflows across hosted and self-hosted endpoints with safer debugging.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-image-plus-sophnet  Qwen Image Plus Sophnet\n  - Generate images via Sophnet Qwen-Image-Plus and poll for task completion. Use when the user asks for Sophnet image generation, Qwen-Image-Plus, or requests an image from the Sophnet API.\nGenerate images via Sophnet Qwen-Image-Plus and poll for task completion. Use when the user asks for Sophnet image generation, Qwen-Image-Plus, or requests an image from the Sophnet API.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-image-skill  qwenz-image-gen\n  - Generate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\nGenerate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen3-tts-instruct  Qwen3 TTS Instruct\n  - Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen TTS with voice/mood presets\nAlibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen TTS with voice/mood presets\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwenz-image-gen  qwenz-image-gen\n  - Generate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\nGenerate images using Alibaba Cloud Bailian Qwen-Image and Z-Image models (通义千图文生图 + 人像照片模型)\n  - version: 1.0.1\nqwenspeak  qwenspeak\n  - Text-to-speech generation via Qwen3-TTS over SSH. Preset voices, voice cloning, voice design. Use when the user wants to generate speech audio, clone voices,...\nText-to-speech generation via Qwen3-TTS over SSH. Preset voices, voice cloning, voice design. Use when the user wants to generate speech audio, clone voices,...\n  - version: 1.5.0\nqwen-video  Qwen Video (Wan)\n  - Generate videos using Alibaba Cloud DashScope Wan (通义万相) text-to-video (t2v) API (e.g., wan2.6-t2v). Use when the user asks to create a short video from a te...\nGenerate videos using Alibaba Cloud DashScope Wan (通义万相) text-to-video (t2v) API (e.g., wan2.6-t2v). Use when the user asks to create a short video from a te...\n  - version: 1.1.0\nqwen-code-skill  Qwen Code\n  - Run Alibaba Cloud Qwen Code CLI via background process for task execution, code review, and automation.\nRun Alibaba Cloud Qwen Code CLI via background process for task execution, code review, and automation.\n  - version: 1.2.0\nqwen3-tts-voicedesign  Qwen3-TTS VoiceDesign\n  - Text-to-speech with Qwen3-TTS VoiceDesign. Design custom voices via natural language descriptions + seed-based timbre fixation. Includes OpenAI-compatible AP...\nText-to-speech with Qwen3-TTS VoiceDesign. Design custom voices via natural language descriptions + seed-based timbre fixation. Includes OpenAI-compatible AP...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-asr  🎤 Transcribe audio files using Qwen ASR. 千问STT\n  - Transcribe audio files using Qwen ASR (千问STT). Use when the user sends voice messages and wants them converted to text.\nTranscribe audio files using Qwen ASR (千问STT). Use when the user sends voice messages and wants them converted to text.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen3-audio  Qwen3 Audio\n  - High-performance audio library for Apple Silicon with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\nHigh-performance audio library for Apple Silicon with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\n  - version: 0.1.1\nqwen-audio  Qwen Audio\n  - High-performance audio library with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\nHigh-performance audio library with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\n  - version: 0.0.6\nqwen3-tts-mlx  Qwen3 Tts Mlx\n  - Local Qwen3-TTS speech synthesis on Apple Silicon via MLX. Use for offline narration, audiobooks, video voiceovers, and multilingual TTS.\nLocal Qwen3-TTS speech synthesis on Apple Silicon via MLX. Use for offline narration, audiobooks, video voiceovers, and multilingual TTS.\n  - version: 2.1.0\nqwen3-tts-feishu  Qwen3-TTS + Feishu Voice\n  - 使用 Qwen3-TTS 本地语音合成，将文字转为语音文件，并可通过飞书发送语音消息（语音气泡格式）。支持 Apple Silicon (MPS) 和 CUDA GPU，无需 API Key 即可本地合成。\n使用 Qwen3-TTS 本地语音合成，将文字转为语音文件，并可通过飞书发送语音消息（语音气泡格式）。支持 Apple Silicon (MPS) 和 CUDA GPU，无需 API Key 即可本地合成。\n  - version: 1.0.3\nqwen-auto-register  Fully automatic Qwen registration, achieving unlimited cup renewals, with timed detection for fully automatic registration\n  - 自动注册 Qwen 账号并获取 token。支持预测性自动切换，避免 API 额度超限。需要安装 auto-register 包。\n自动注册 Qwen 账号并获取 token。支持预测性自动切换，避免 API 额度超限。需要安装 auto-register 包。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nqwen-asr-skill  Qwen Asr Skill\n  - Provides high-accuracy speech-to-text conversion supporting 22 Chinese dialects and 30 languages with automatic language detection, running on CPU.\nProvides high-accuracy speech-to-text conversion supporting 22 Chinese dialects and 30 languages with automatic language detection, running on CPU.\n  - version: 1.3.0\nms-qwen-vl  Ms Qwen Vl\n  - 调用魔搭社区（ModelScope）Qwen3-VL 多模态 API 进行视觉解析。使用 OpenAI SDK 兼容方式调用，支持图片内容描述、OCR 文字提取、视觉问答、对象检测等功能。用户提到\"魔搭\"、\"ModelScope\"、\"Qwen-VL\"、\"多模态视觉\"、\"解析图片\"等关键词时应触发。\n调用魔搭社区（ModelScope）Qwen3-VL 多模态 API 进行视觉解析。使用 OpenAI SDK 兼容方式调用，支持图片内容描述、OCR 文字提取、视觉问答、对象检测等功能。用户提到\"魔搭\"、\"ModelScope\"、\"Qwen-VL\"、\"多模态视觉\"、\"解析图片\"等关键词时应触发。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nfree-voice  Free voice from Comfy UI +  Qwen3 TTS\n  - Generate Russian male voice audio using ComfyUI with Qwen3 TTS node and save as MP3 for voice messages.\nGenerate Russian male voice audio using ComfyUI with Qwen3 TTS node and save as MP3 for voice messages.\n  - version: 1.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":730,"aggregated":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nqwen-image  Qwen Image\n  - Generate images using Qwen Image API (Alibaba Cloud DashScope). Use when users request image generation with Chinese prompts or need high-quality AI-generated images from text descriptions.\n使用通义万相API（阿里云DashScope）生成图像。适用于中文提示词图像生成或基于文本描述生成高质量AI图像的场景。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-tts  Qwen3-tts\n  - Local text-to-speech using Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-CustomVoice. Use when generating audio from text, creating voice messages, or when TTS is requested. Supports 10 languages including Italian, 9 premium speaker voices, and instruction-based voice control (emotion, tone, style). Alternative to cloud-based TTS services like ElevenLabs. Runs entirely offline after initial model download.\nLocal text-to-speech using Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-CustomVoice. Use when generating audio from text, creating voice messages, or when TTS is requested. Supports 10 languages including Italian, 9 premium speaker voices, and instruction-based voice control (emotion, tone, style). Alternative to cloud-based TTS services like ElevenLabs. Runs entirely offline after 