 when the user asks to create a short video from a te...\n  - version: 1.1.0\nqwen-code-skill  Qwen Code\n  - Run Alibaba Cloud Qwen Code CLI via background process for task execution, code review, and automation.\nRun Alibaba Cloud Qwen Code CLI via background process for task execution, code review, and automation.\n  - version: 1.2.0\nqwen3-tts-voicedesign  Qwen3-TTS VoiceDesign\n  - Text-to-speech with Qwen3-TTS VoiceDesign. Design custom voices via natural language descriptions + seed-based timbre fixation. Includes OpenAI-compatible AP...\nText-to-speech with Qwen3-TTS VoiceDesign. Design custom voices via natural language descriptions + seed-based timbre fixation. Includes OpenAI-compatible AP...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen-asr  🎤 Transcribe audio files using Qwen ASR. 千问STT\n  - Transcribe audio files using Qwen ASR (千问STT). Use when the user sends voice messages and wants them converted to text.\nTranscribe audio files using Qwen ASR (千问STT). Use when the user sends voice messages and wants them converted to text.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nqwen3-audio  Qwen3 Audio\n  - High-performance audio library for Apple Silicon with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\nHigh-performance audio library for Apple Silicon with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\n  - version: 0.1.1\nqwen-audio  Qwen Audio\n  - High-performance audio library with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\nHigh-performance audio library with text-to-speech (TTS) and speech-to-text (STT).\n  - version: 0.0.6\nqwen3-tts-mlx  Qwen3 Tts Mlx\n  - Local Qwen3-TTS speech synthesis on Apple Silicon via MLX. Use for offline narration, audiobooks, video voiceovers, and multilingual TTS.\nLocal Qwen3-TTS speech synthesis on Apple Silicon via MLX. Use for offline narration, audiobooks, video voiceovers, and multilingual TTS.\n  - version: 2.1.0\nqwen3-tts-feishu  Qwen3-TTS + Feishu Voice\n  - 使用 Qwen3-TTS 本地语音合成，将文字转为语音文件，并可通过飞书发送语音消息（语音气泡格式）。支持 Apple Silicon (MPS) 和 CUDA GPU，无需 API Key 即可本地合成。\n使用 Qwen3-TTS 本地语音合成，将文字转为语音文件，并可通过飞书发送语音消息（语音气泡格式）。支持 Apple Silicon (MPS) 和 CUDA GPU，无需 API Key 即可本地合成。\n  - version: 1.0.3\nqwen-auto-register  Fully automatic Qwen registration, achieving unlimited cup renewals, with timed detection for fully automatic registration\n  - 自动注册 Qwen 账号并获取 token。支持预测性自动切换，避免 API 额度超限。需要安装 auto-register 包。\n自动注册 Qwen 账号并获取 token。支持预测性自动切换，避免 API 额度超限。需要安装 auto-register 包。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nqwen-asr-skill  Qwen Asr Skill\n  - Provides high-accuracy speech-to-text conversion supporting 22 Chinese dialects and 30 languages with automatic language detection, running on CPU.\nProvides high-accuracy speech-to-text conversion supporting 22 Chinese dialects and 30 languages with automatic language detection, running on CPU.\n  - version: 1.3.0\nms-qwen-vl  Ms Qwen Vl\n  - 调用魔搭社区（ModelScope）Qwen3-VL 多模态 API 进行视觉解析。使用 OpenAI SDK 兼容方式调用，支持图片内容描述、OCR 文字提取、视觉问答、对象检测等功能。用户提到\"魔搭\"、\"ModelScope\"、\"Qwen-VL\"、\"多模态视觉\"、\"解析图片\"等关键词时应触发。\n调用魔搭社区（ModelScope）Qwen3-VL 多模态 API 进行视觉解析。使用 OpenAI SDK 兼容方式调用，支持图片内容描述、OCR 文字提取、视觉问答、对象检测等功能。用户提到\"魔搭\"、\"ModelScope\"、\"Qwen-VL\"、\"多模态视觉\"、\"解析图片\"等关键词时应触发。\n  - version: 0.1.0\nfree-voice  Free voice from Comfy UI +  Qwen3 TTS\n  - Generate Russian male voice audio using ComfyUI with Qwen3 TTS node and save as MP3 for voice messages.\nGenerate Russian male voice audio using ComfyUI with Qwen3 TTS node and save as MP3 for voice messages.\n  - version: 1.0.0","cwd":"/Users/liyue/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773741286917}}
{"type":"message","id":"b3c27c12","parentId":"4d1c928b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:54:59.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搜索结果找到了 qwen 相关的技能，有一个基础的 `qwen` 技能（版本 1.0.0），用于构建和路由 Qwen 工作流。但是没有直接找到 Qwen3.5-4B 本地安装的专用技能。\n\n**搜索结果摘要：**\n- **来源**: SkillHub 商店\n- **找到**: 21 个 qwen 相关技能\n- **最匹配**: `qwen` 基础技能 v1.0.0，用于构建和路由 Qwen 工作流\n\n**问题**: SkillHub 上没有专门用于\"本地安装 Qwen3.5-4B\"的技能。Qwen3.5-4B 本身是一个 AI 模型，需要通过 llama.cpp、ollama 或 mlx-lm 等本地推理框架运行。\n\n让我搜索一下 ollama 相关技能看看：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1rhs70ruq5z6h3nq3x6p654r","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"skillhub search ollama 2>&1","shell":"zsh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773741286924}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd3a98c6","parentId":"b3c27c12","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:55:00.772Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1rhs70ruq5z6h3nq3x6p654r","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nollama  Ollama\n  - Run, tune, and troubleshoot local Ollama models with reliable API patterns, Modelfiles, embeddings, and hardware-aware deployment workflows.\nRun, tune, and troubleshoot local Ollama models with reliable API patterns, Modelfiles, embeddings, and hardware-aware deployment workflows.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-local  Ollama Local\n  - Manage and use local Ollama models. Use for model management (list/pull/remove), chat/completions, embeddings, and tool-use with local LLMs. Covers OpenClaw sub-agent integration and model selection guidance.\n管理本地Ollama模型，支持模型管理（列出/拉取/删除）、聊天/补全、嵌入及工具调用，集成OpenClaw子代理并提供模型选择指导。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nollama-memory-embeddings  Ollama Memory Embeddings\n  - Configure OpenClaw memory search to use Ollama as the embeddings server (OpenAI-compatible /v1/embeddings) instead of the built-in node-llama-cpp local GGUF loading. Includes interactive model selection and optional import of an existing local embedding GGUF into Ollama.\nConfigure OpenClaw memory search to use Ollama as the embeddings server (OpenAI-compatible /v1/embeddings) instead of the built-in node-llama-cpp local GGUF loading. Includes interactive model selection and optional import of an existing local embedding GGUF into Ollama.\n  - version: 1.0.4\nollama-x-z-image-turbo  Image Generation (Ollama x/z-image-turbo · macOS only)\n  - Génère une image en local via Ollama x/z-image-turbo sur macOS et l'envoie sur WhatsApp selon le prompt donné.\nGénère une image en local via Ollama x/z-image-turbo sur macOS et l'envoie sur WhatsApp selon le prompt donné.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-updater  Ollama Updater\n  - Ollama Updater installs or updates Ollama with curl-based breakpoint resume, auto-retry, progress display, old version cleanup, and GPU driver detection.\nOllama Updater installs or updates Ollama with curl-based breakpoint resume, auto-retry, progress display, old version cleanup, and GPU driver detection.\n  - version: 1.0.1\nollama-model-tuner  Ollama Model Tuner\n  - Locally fine-tune Ollama models, prompts, and LoRAs using custom datasets and evaluation metrics without requiring cloud resources.\nLocally fine-tune Ollama models, prompts, and LoRAs using custom datasets and evaluation metrics without requiring cloud resources.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-integration  Ollama Integration\n  - Integrate and run local Ollama AI models with custom prompts for AI assistance and automatic model management.\nIntegrate and run local Ollama AI models with custom prompts for AI assistance and automatic model management.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-web-search  Ollama Web Search\n  - Web search via Ollama API. Returns relevant results from Ollama web search for AI agents.\nWeb search via Ollama API. Returns relevant results from Ollama web search for AI agents.\n  - version: 1.0.1\nollama-vision  ollama-vision\n  - 本地调用 Ollama qwen3-vl:4b 模型自动压缩并分析图片，支持描述、OCR 文字提取和自定义信息抽取。\n本地调用 Ollama qwen3-vl:4b 模型自动压缩并分析图片，支持描述、OCR 文字提取和自定义信息抽取。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-memory  Ollama Memory\n  - 本地向量记忆系统 - 基于 Ollama + SQLite 的 AI 助手记忆方案。 支持：Markdown 记录、向量搜索、本地嵌入、无 API 费用。 特点：本地部署、语义搜索、隐私优先。\n本地向量记忆系统 - 基于 Ollama + SQLite 的 AI 助手记忆方案。 支持：Markdown 记录、向量搜索、本地嵌入、无 API 费用。 特点：本地部署、语义搜索、隐私优先。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ntoken-optimizer  Tokenoptimizer\n  - Reduce OpenClaw AI costs by 97%. Haiku model routing, free Ollama heartbeats, prompt caching, and budget controls. Go from $1,500/month to $50/month in 5 min...\nOpenClaw AI 成本降低 97%，支持 Haiku 模型路由、免费 Ollama 保活、提示词缓存和预算控制。5 分钟内月费从 $1,500 降至 $50。\n  - version: 1.0.18\nchromadb-memory  Chromadb Memory Pub\n  - Long-term memory via ChromaDB with local Ollama embeddings. Auto-recall injects relevant context every turn. No cloud APIs required — fully self-hosted.\n基于ChromaDB与本地Ollama嵌入的长期记忆，每轮自动召回并注入相关上下文。无需云端API，完全自托管。\n  - version: 1.2.1\nchat-ollama-gradio  Pywayne Llm Chat Ollama Gradio\n  - Gradio-based chat interface for Ollama with multi-session management. Use when working with pywayne.llm.chat_ollama_gradio module to create a web-based chat...\nGradio-based chat interface for Ollama with multi-session management. Use when working with pywayne.llm.chat_ollama_gradio module to create a web-based chat...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nllm-supervisor  LLM Supervisor\n  - Graceful rate limit handling with Ollama fallback. Notifies on rate limits, offers local model switch with confirmation for code tasks.\nGraceful rate limit handling with Ollama fallback. Notifies on rate limits, offers local model switch with confirmation for code tasks.\n  - version: 0.3.0\nllmrouter  Llmrouter\n  - Intelligent LLM proxy that routes requests to appropriate models based on complexity. Save money by using cheaper models for simple tasks. Tested with Anthropic, OpenAI, Gemini, Kimi/Moonshot, and Ollama.\nIntelligent LLM proxy that routes requests to appropriate models based on complexity. Save money by using cheaper models for simple tasks. Tested with Anthropic, OpenAI, Gemini, Kimi/Moonshot, and Ollama.\n  - version: 0.1.1\nemail-triage  email-triage\n  - IMAP email scanning and triage with AI classification via a local Ollama LLM. Scans unread emails, categorizes them as urgent, needs-response, informational,...\nIMAP email scanning and triage with AI classification via a local Ollama LLM. Scans unread emails, categorizes them as urgent, needs-response, informational,...\n  - version: 1.0.1\ncomanda  Comanda\n  - Generate, visualize, and execute declarative AI pipelines using the comanda CLI. Use when creating LLM workflows from natural language, viewing workflow charts, editing YAML workflow files, or processing/running comanda workflows. Supports multi-model orchestration (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Ollama, Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Codex).\nGenerate, visualize, and execute declarative AI pipelines using the comanda CLI. Use when creating LLM workflows from natural language, viewing workflow charts, editing YAML workflow files, or processing/running comanda workflows. Supports multi-model orchestration (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Ollama, Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Codex).\n  - version: 1.0.2\nengram  Engram\n  - Persistent semantic memory layer for AI agents. Local-first storage (SQLite+LanceDB) with Ollama embeddings. Store and recall facts, decisions, preferences, events, relationships across sessions. Supports memory decay, deduplication, typed memories (5 types), memory relationships (7 graph relation types), agent/user scoping, semantic search, context-aware recall, auto-extraction from text (rules/LLM/hybrid), import/export, REST API, MCP protocol. Solves context window and compaction amnesia. Server at localhost:3400, dashboard at /dashboard. Install via npm (engram-memory), requires Ollama with nomic-embed-text model.\nPersistent semantic memory layer for AI agents. Local-first storage (SQLite+LanceDB) with Ollama embeddings. Store and recall facts, decisions, preferences, events, relationships across sessions. Supports memory decay, deduplication, typed memories (5 types), memory relationships (7 graph relation types), agent/user scoping, semantic search, context-aware recall, auto-extraction from text (rules/LLM/hybrid), import/export, REST API, MCP protocol. Solves context window and compaction amnesia. Server at localhost:3400, dashboard at /dashboard. Install via npm (engram-memory), requires Ollama with nomic-embed-text model.\n  - version: 0.2.1\nstrands  Strands Agents SDK\n  - Build and run Python-based AI agents using the AWS Strands SDK. Use when you need to create autonomous agents, multi-agent workflows, custom tools, or integrate with MCP servers. Supports Ollama (local), Anthropic, OpenAI, Bedrock, and other model providers. Use for agent scaffolding, tool creation, and running agent tasks programmatically.\nBuild and run Python-based AI agents using the AWS Strands SDK. Use when you need to create autonomous agents, multi-agent workflows, custom tools, or integrate with MCP servers. Supports Ollama (local), Anthropic, OpenAI, Bedrock, and other model providers. Use for agent scaffolding, tool creation, and running agent tasks programmatically.\n  - version: 2.0.3\naws-strands  Strands\n  - Build and run Python-based AI agents using the AWS Strands SDK. Use when you need to create autonomous agents, multi-agent workflows, custom tools, or integrate with MCP servers. Supports Ollama (local), Anthropic, OpenAI, Bedrock, and other model providers. Use for agent scaffolding, tool creation, and running agent tasks programmatically.\nBuild and run Python-based AI agents using the AWS Strands SDK. Use when you need to create autonomous agents, multi-agent workflows, custom tools, or integrate with MCP servers. Supports Ollama (local), Anthropic, OpenAI, Bedrock, and other model providers. Use for agent scaffolding, tool creation, and running agent tasks programmatically.\n  - version: 1.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":804,"aggregated":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nollama  Ollama\n  - Run, tune, and troubleshoot local Ollama models with reliable API patterns, Modelfiles, embeddings, and hardware-aware deployment workflows.\nRun, tune, and troubleshoot local Ollama models with reliable API patterns, Modelfiles, embeddings, and hardware-aware deployment workflows.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nollama-local  Ollama Local\n  - Manage and use local Ollama models. Use for model management (list/pull/remove), chat/completions, embeddings, and tool-use with local LLMs. Covers OpenClaw sub-agent integration and model selection guidance.\n管理本地Ollama模型，支持模型管理（列出/拉取/删除）、聊天/补全、嵌入及工具调用，集成OpenClaw子代理并提供模型选择指导。\n  - version: 1.1.0\nollama-memory-embeddings  Ollama Memory Embeddings\n  - 